title: Autumn Glass Pumpkin—Confetti
description:
Delicate, graceful hand-blown glass breathes life into a beloved icon of the fall season. A stem falling into curly tendrils adds character to these glistening pumpkins in shades of pink, white, green, and blue. Made exclusively in the USA, and individually signed by the artist, no two are alike. 

7 1/2 x 5 in. diam.
